System Design for Accounting SaaS Dashboard

1. Required Modules
Based on the provided documents (SRS, Source Code Structure, and Implementation Plan), the system requires the following modules:

1.1. Core Modules
App Management Module: Manages application initialization, configuration, and navigation.
Data Processing Module: Processes, transforms, and calculates financial data.
Authentication Module: Handles user authentication and access control.
1.2. Feature Modules
Transaction Search Module: Searches and filters transactions (FR-04).
Financial Overview Module: Displays financial summaries (FR-01).
Report Generation Module: Creates and exports financial reports (FR-05).
1.3. UI Modules
Component Module: Provides reusable UI components.
Layout Module: Defines page layouts for different features.
Style Module: Manages UI styling and design.
1.4. Utility Modules
Export Module: Exports data in various formats (CSV, PDF).
Calculation Module: Includes financial calculation functions.
Configuration Module: Manages system settings and configurations.